# Applies when the Docker build context is ./src (the shared-module-consuming Go
# services — see docker-compose.yml). Keeps the context small even though it now
# spans the whole src tree: only go.mod/go.sum + Go source are needed to build a
# service plus the ../shared replace targets.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/coverage
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/.vite
**/.next
**/playwright-report
**/test-results
**/.git
**/*.log
